00:30:33.360 --> 00:30:36.250
I've come to completely
change my view on this.

00:30:36.250 --> 00:30:40.240
And in fact, at one point, we've
gotten to 1,000 entrepreneurs

00:30:40.240 --> 00:30:40.740
