they were working in

00:30:45.134 --> 00:30:47.050
and their backgrounds,
but in their approaches

00:30:47.050 --> 00:30:48.930
as leaders and their
strengths and weaknesses.

00:30:48.930 --> 00:30:50.930
And yet they were all
trying to model themselves

00:30:50.930 --> 00:30:51.900
after Steve Jobs.

00:30:51.900 --> 00:30:53.260
And I was like, but
this isn't working.

00:30:53.260 --> 00:30:55.510
You have different strengths
and different weaknesses.

00:30:55.510 --> 00:30:58.050
So I worked with Bain &amp;
Company for three years

00:30:58.050 --> 00:30:59.709
on an entrepreneur
personality test.

00:30:59.709 --> 00:31:01.500
It's really a personality
test as a leader.

00:31:01.500 --> 00:31:03.416
You can go download it
at lindarottenberg.com,

00:31:03.416 --> 00:31:05.330
a shortened version.

00:31:05.330 --> 00:31:07.950
And what we realized, we came
up with four personality types.

00:31:07.950 --> 00:31:11.220
These are different
from my species.

00:31:11.220 --> 00:31:14.300
So the rocket ships
are people who

00:31:14.300 --> 00:31:16.600
really care about
efficiency and metrics

00:31:16.600 --> 00:31:19.490
and taking things that work
and making them even better.

00:31:19.490 --> 00:31:23.810
The stars focus on brands
and they're more personality

00:31:23.810 --> 00:31:25.610
driven, often more in the arts.

00:31:25.610 --> 00:31:30.680
Transformers often take older
businesses and modernize them.

00:31:30.680 --> 00:31:34.420
And they're really interested
in both the mission

00:31:34.420 --> 00:31:37.960
of the new businesses, but how
you transform these old school

00:31:37.960 --> 00:31:39.440
products and services.

00:31:39.440 --> 00:31:44.270
And then the diamonds are more
of the classic inventor types.

00:31:44.270 --> 00:31:47.260
And each of these
personalities, as I said,

00:31:47.260 --> 00:31:49.600
has the ability to be the
leader and the entrepreneur,

00:31:49.600 --> 00:31:53.330
but who you surround yourself
as a team, as advisors,

00:31:53.330 --> 00:31:55.440
and as mentors does change.

00:31:55.440 --> 00:31:58.550
So I would encourage you,
take this personality test.

00:31:58.550 --> 00:32:01.295
We have a longer version if
you're really interested.

