00:33:22.880 --> 00:33:24.489
It's people holding
themselves back.

00:33:24.489 --> 00:33:26.030
And you'll find out
soon enough, it's

00:33:26.030 --> 00:33:27.430
all about execution at the end.

00:33:27.430 --> 00:33:29.580
And what I always say is
the marketplace tells you

00:33:29.580 --> 00:33:32.090
soon enough, just don't hold
yourself back initially.

