00:35:07.240 --> 00:35:08.730
and weaknesses as
an entrepreneur,

00:35:08.730 --> 00:35:10.146
and they don't
surround themselves

00:35:10.146 --> 00:35:11.200
with the right people.

00:35:11.200 --> 00:35:14.580
So I go very much into
