00:35:57.200 --> 00:35:58.530
I love that idea too.

00:35:58.530 --> 00:36:00.105
Just getting a
sense of will people

00:36:00.105 --> 00:36:01.480
put their money
where their mouth

00:36:01.480 --> 00:36:04.690
is to know which ideas tend
