I can't wait to read the book.

00:36:10.030 --> 00:36:12.210
I was curious if you could
talk a little bit more

00:36:12.210 --> 00:36:14.020
about the group of
guys in Argentina

00:36:14.020 --> 00:36:16.450
I think that you said made
it through the first round

00:36:16.450 --> 00:36:19.560
and you turned them down
because of perceived arrogance,

00:36:19.560 --> 00:36:23.410
but then the second time
around something clicked there.

00:36:23.410 --> 00:36:25.780
In the context of
your story about how

00:36:25.780 --> 00:36:29.450
you approached that
other investor and said,

00:36:29.450 --> 00:36:31.700
you're lucky I didn't
